,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T18:06:20.000Z","msg":"我果隻係大脾做 的地話咁樣傷口細d 線都唔洗拆 一開頭用膠頭套好嬲 係咁撐兜 一晚起十次第幫佢帶番 後尾有人介紹左隻布既 一直帶到埋口 不過真係要忍心d困籠 周圍跳好危險好易爆傷口"},{"pid":"10b5fca4ec5817b4114529dfadca137fca2676be","tid":81881,"uid":13652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T18:09:18.000Z","msg":"係咁打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我果隻係大脾做 人地話咁樣傷口細d 線都唔洗拆 其實我都係做完先知可以係大脾做 一開頭用膠頭套好嬲 係咁撐甩 一晚起十次身幫佢帶番 後尾有人介紹左隻布既 一直帶到埋口 不過真係要忍心d困籠 周圍跳好危險好易爆傷口"},{"pid":"d81fa0e45197544a6fabd33899a467e9552d6a8b","tid":81881,"uid":5426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T22:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係大圍俊康絕左<br />\n好返中間個傷口腫到成個波咁 嚇到我死 9沖返去睇<br />\n點知原來算正常現象 拆線已經冇左個波<br />\n絕完到拆線個傷口一d血水都冇 應該幾靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇指定醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc31855a3786a401b6c55ad5b172909884af5e01","tid":81881,"uid":5426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T22:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咁打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我果隻係大脾做 人地話咁樣傷口細d 線都唔洗拆 其實我都係做完先知可以係大脾做 一開頭用膠頭套好嬲 係咁撐甩 一晚起十次身幫佢帶番 後尾有人介紹左隻布既 一直帶到埋口 不過真係要忍心d困籠 周圍跳好危險好易爆傷口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗住用布頭套"},{"pid":"27ec23f62a6dc99278358399867b609bd847400a","tid":81881,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"最近兩隻女喺spca做左自動線嗰隻<br />\n邊間診所俾唔到意見<br />\n但事後保養可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地戴勁套勁反抗，所以淘左件貓女用手術服<br />\n(買一件番嚟跟住diy)<br />\n好似肚兜咁遮住傷口<br />\n郁動無咁方便，減低疤痕<br />\n最緊要番工無人睇住都可以食嘢飲水又唔驚個套甩<br />\n同埋唔阻佢地清理自己<br />\n藍色係淘嗰件，之後用舊衫整左幾件替換<br />\nPet pet位整大啲屙屎都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/091912_1a977ee29df8d1cc79d577ea4f989fc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F091912_1a977ee29df8d1cc79d577ea4f989fc8.jpg&h=eaed68e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/16/091914_84ba6ff758945cadc5a6386babc56de1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F091914_84ba6ff758945cadc5a6386babc56de1.jpg&h=b1a712e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我無困籠但細嗰隻少郁都ok，而家已經退紅<br />\n大嘅成日衝所以有啲疤<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeR6JU6DVgNykuSNXmV6bGgGQEDxUjN8H47EpYNwvzu15?filename=8ReE7Fj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ReE7Fj.jpg&h=d5859d6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8a8083caa121b85515b38e01e077d2cf275fa6d","tid":81881,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"絕完要睇住佢由其屙屎嗰陣<br />\n衰女去屙屎<br />\n啲屎插到成個燈罩都係<br />\n結果搞到成屋屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c76e32197c5f887706111dae4f0fcb898462c7","tid":81881,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係大圍俊康絕左<br />\n好返中間個傷口腫到成個波咁 嚇到我死 9沖返去睇<br />\n點知原來算正常現象 拆線已經冇左個波<br />\n絕完到拆線個傷口一d血水都冇 應該幾靚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇指定醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n闕醫生 不過d診所姑娘態度.,,"},{"pid":"184ceb7d75ec8a548464012569ca43182c131c9b","tid":81881,"uid":31918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"用唔用溶線其實睇情況"},{"pid":"99ab1d6415d453caceade7b6011b9c51607e917f","tid":81881,"uid":52490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"184ceb7d75ec8a548464012569ca43182c131c9b","tid":81881,"uid":31918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"用唔用溶線其實睇情況"},